Email: thymuoyhak.biu@gmail.com

Postal Address: [Insert Address]

12. Reviewing or Deleting Your Data
To request access to, update, or delete your personal information, please submit a data subject access request using the contact details above. Applicable laws may limit these rights in certain circumstances.
